node.text:
Understanding different asset classes can be key for long-term success

For beginners, @Robbywclark recommends matching your liability expenses with your asset purchases💰

Here's Robby's breakdown of different asset classes he likes for long-term success:

1. Real estate. Buy a property and rent it out. That’ll help pay down equity while also having a consistent cash flow🏡

2. Stocks are a traditional investment vehicle. Historically they tend to be a safe investment over the long run that will accumulate big returns over time.

3. I love cryptocurrencies, but to an old-school investor they would be considered risky, so limit your exposure when starting, but don’t miss out!

4. Whole/universal life insurance policies can also be a great investment vehicle and are utilized by savvy investors as well as ultra-high network individuals to invest in their future

@TheIdealCard The Smartest Business Card In The World
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@TheIdealCard Smart Contactless #DigitalBusinessCards by @INKGILITY
⁣⁣
The Reinvention of the #BusinessCard is Finally Here thanks to @INKGILITY⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Tap into the Future of #BusinessCards with @TheIdealCard, A Smart #Contactless #DigitalBusinessCard for The Digital Age.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@TheIdealCard is a chip embedded instrument that triggers an Add to Contacts action on Compatible #Smartphones such as an #iPhone & #Android phone displaying voluminous, just transferred contact details in a matter of seconds.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
You can transfer details such as your Name, Company Name, A Photo or Logo, Email Address, Phone Number(s), Website, Physical Address with directions from Google Maps, Social Media Profiles & Instant Messaging Profiles, Payment Profiles, Emergency Contact Information, Videos, Music, Shopping Pages, an Elevator Pitch, Upcoming Events, and much more.⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@TheIdealCard comes as a card, ring, key holder, wallet, smartphone sticky, and many more items for added convenience.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣

for newcomers getting started:

1. Get started

2. Energy goes where revenue flows-If you’re gonna spend $200 on shoes, the bar, a handbag, then invest $200 in stocks or another asset. Match your liability expenses with assets purchases

node.text:
There is no better way to start September than to start it with a new @Skeletonconceptofficial. And gosh did they deliver!
 
Let us introduce you to the #Maldonado Concept timepiece, a special design made for the @F1 Venezuelan racing driver, @pastormaldo - Pastor Maldonado.
This spectacular timepiece pushes the limits and the codes of the Daytona 116520 furthermore, thanks to its skeletonized design and the stunning and very elegant blue-ish & grey palette tones used on the dial. The bezel - in 5 grade Titanium (the highest level of quality for this material)  gives it a smooth and minimalist aspect.
 
We can’t quite put our finger on it? Is it the combination of the high standard “bleu horloger” with the matte Oyster steel bracelet, the sharp handmade bevelling of the movement or something else entirely - but this timepiece definitely has something more than the others. It unequivocally reminds us of racing cars and  Formula One.
 
A demonstration of the finest watchmaking and haute horology.
 
WE LOVE IT.
_________________________________
Skeleton Concept is a handcraft atelier that specializes in watch customization.
They neither manufacture and/or sell timepieces. Skeleton Concept is not affiliated, associated, authorized, endorsed by, or in any way officially connected with Rolex SA or any of its subsidiaries.  The personalization of the watches are carried out meticulously while staying true to the essence of the original brand manufacturers.
